category=Useful Techniques
description=<p>Many applications you write may need a menu bar.  This tutorial introduces you to the Menu Builder which allows you to create and script a menu bar for your application.</p>
duration=6:50
filename=menu_bars.avi
level=2
licensed=true
name=Menu Bars
scripts=<p><font color="#000000">Scripts Used in this Tutorial:</font></p>\n<p></p>\n<p><font face="Courier New" size="12" color="#000000">on menuPick pWhich</font></p>\n<p><font face="Courier New" size="12" color="#000000">  switch pWhich</font></p>\n<p><font face="Courier New" size="12" color="#000000">  case &quot;New&quot;</font></p>\n<p><font face="Courier New" size="12" color="#000000">    create stack</font></p>\n<p><font face="Courier New" size="12" color="#000000">    break</font></p>\n<p><font face="Courier New" size="12" color="#000000">  case &quot;Open&quot;</font></p>\n<p><font face="Courier New" size="12" color="#000000">    answer file &quot;Select a Stack:&quot;</font></p>\n<p><font face="Courier New" size="12" color="#000000">    go stack it</font></p>\n<p><font face="Courier New" size="12" color="#000000">    break</font></p>\n<p><font face="Courier New" size="12" color="#000000">  case &quot;Save&quot;</font></p>\n<p><font face="Courier New" size="12" color="#000000">    save this stack</font></p>\n<p><font face="Courier New" size="12" color="#000000">    break</font></p>\n<p><font face="Courier New" size="12" color="#000000">  case &quot;Close&quot;</font></p>\n<p><font face="Courier New" size="12" color="#000000">    close this stack</font></p>\n<p><font face="Courier New" size="12" color="#000000">    break</font></p>\n<p><font face="Courier New" size="12" color="#000000">  case &quot;Quit&quot;</font></p>\n<p><font face="Courier New" size="12" color="#000000">    quit</font></p>\n<p><font face="Courier New" size="12" color="#000000">    break</font></p>\n<p><font face="Courier New" size="12" color="#000000">  end switch</font></p>\n<p><font face="Courier New" size="12" color="#000000">end menuPick</font></p>\n<p></p>\n<p><font face="Courier New" size="12" color="#000000">on menuPick pWhich</font></p>\n<p><font face="Courier New" size="12" color="#000000">  switch pWhich</font></p>\n<p><font face="Courier New" size="12" color="#000000">  case &quot;Cut&quot;</font></p>\n<p><font face="Courier New" size="12" color="#000000">    cut</font></p>\n<p><font face="Courier New" size="12" color="#000000">    break</font></p>\n<p><font face="Courier New" size="12" color="#000000">  case &quot;Copy&quot;</font></p>\n<p><font face="Courier New" size="12" color="#000000">    copy</font></p>\n<p><font face="Courier New" size="12" color="#000000">    break</font></p>\n<p><font face="Courier New" size="12" color="#000000">  case &quot;Paste&quot;</font></p>\n<p><font face="Courier New" size="12" color="#000000">    paste</font></p>\n<p><font face="Courier New" size="12" color="#000000">    break</font></p>\n<p><font face="Courier New" size="12" color="#000000">  case &quot;Clear&quot;</font></p>\n<p><font face="Courier New" size="12" color="#000000">    delete</font></p>\n<p><font face="Courier New" size="12" color="#000000">    break</font></p>\n<p><font face="Courier New" size="12" color="#000000">  end switch</font></p>\n<p><font face="Courier New" size="12" color="#000000">end menuPick</font></p>\n<p></p>\n<p><font face="Courier New" size="12" color="#000000">on menuPick pWhich</font></p>\n<p><font face="Courier New" size="12" color="#000000">  switch pWhich</font></p>\n<p><font face="Courier New" size="12" color="#000000">  case &quot;About&quot;</font></p>\n<p><font face="Courier New" size="12" color="#000000">    answer &quot;This is my program version 1.0.&quot;</font></p>\n<p><font face="Courier New" size="12" color="#000000">    break</font></p>\n<p><font face="Courier New" size="12" color="#000000">  end switch</font></p>\n<p><font face="Courier New" size="12" color="#000000">end menuPick</font></p>
title=Menu Bars: creating and editing using the Menu Builder
topics=<p>Key Topics Covered in this Tutorial:</p>\n<p>-&#9;The Menu Builder makes it easy to create a menu bar with menus and menu items</p>\n<p>-&#9;This menu bar will display correctly on different types of computer</p>\n<p>-&#9;How to create a standard menu bar with File, Edit and Help</p>\n<p>-&#9;Adding simple scripts to make the menu bar work</p>\n<p>-&#9;Special considerations if youre running Mac OS</p>\n<p>-  Editing your menus later</p>